headline: ViCentra to Bring Smartphone-Based Closed Loop Therapy to People with Diabetes in Early 2026
summary: ViCentra, maker of the Kaleido insulin patch pump, today announced that following the CE Mark approval of Diabeloop's DBLG2 algorithm under the EU Medical Device Regulation (MDR), its next-generation hybrid closed loop system is set to launch in Germany and the Netherlands in early 2026.
